## cache_httpfs

Delegate the block cache / parallel range IO / eviction to `cache_httpfs`
(community, "drop-in replacement for httpfs"). It only helps reads that go through
DuckDB's VFS — which `.pgen` does **not** today — so it is unlocked *by* the shim,
not a substitute for it. Our shim keeps only the pgen-format-specific
offset-index range planning. Load it in the milestone-3 spike or the cached case
is under-measured.
